# After Workflow Engine

- Enterprise Super Apps MUST load workflow definitions from
  `assets/workflows/catalog.json` (or equivalent) and/or Remote Config
  key `after.workflow.catalog` via `hydrateWorkflowCatalog`.
- Do not hard-code workflow graphs in product Dart for each admission,
  flight prep, port arrival, machine repair, etc.
- Every business-process state change goes through
  `WorkflowEngine.transition` / `WorkflowRepository.applyTransition`.
- Gate UI actions with RBAC; the engine re-checks
  `requiredPermission` / `requiredRole`.
- Docs: `docs/WORKFLOW_ENGINE.md`. Examples under `examples/workflows/`.
